08:19.440 --> 08:25.200
Clark has a reputation as a hard science writer, but what strikes me as most interesting

08:25.200 --> 08:32.420
about his work is the color and invention of alien situations and surroundings and characters

08:32.420 --> 08:33.840
in City and the Star.

08:34.400 --> 08:39.920
