I reread the story immediately after reading it once, and I'll do that still to things.

12:27.520 --> 12:29.680
There are great many stories that I drag off the shelf.

12:29.780 --> 12:32.420
I drag off the Hell Clements stories periodically from the shelf.

12:32.420 --> 12:33.620
The best of those.

12:34.000 --> 12:36.860
Mission of Gravity, Cycle of Fire.

12:37.060 --> 12:37.980
Cycle of Fire, particularly.

12:38.580 --> 12:39.540
That's a magical thought.

